-- Murray & Roberts Zimbabwe Plans Name Change, Daily News Says
-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 2012-11-17T09:40:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-17/murray-roberts-zimbabwe-plans-name-change-daily-news-says.html
Construction company  Murray &
Roberts Zimbabwe Ltd. (MAR)  will seek shareholder approval to change
its name to Masimba Holdings Ltd., the Daily News said, citing a
company statement.  The name change follows the sale of 46.5 percent of the
company held by South Africa’s  Murray & Roberts Holdings Ltd. (MUR)  to
Zumbani Capital (Pvt) Ltd., the Harare-based Daily News said on
its  website . Shareholders will be asked to approve the name
change at the company’s annual general meeting Dec. 13 in
Harare, the newspaper reported, citing the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at 
 blatham@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria in Johannesburg at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net . 